Description:
Modern Family Home Around Corner From Shopping Centre!
This beautiful family home located just around corner from Dandenong Plaza and Dandenong Primary School, close to St Marys School, St Johns College, Dandenong Station and central to all amenities. If you are looking for the perfect home in perfect location, it doesn't come better than this.
In great condition, this appealing townhouse will delight with all the comforts and spaciousness a family could ever want. Entertaining family and friends will be an absolute must with its generous sized living zones.
Featuring:
- 3 bedrooms all with BIR's and master with Full Ensuite and WIR
- Spacious gourmet kitchen with Island bench top and gas appliances
- Open plan living an abundance of natural light
- Open kitchen/meals area, opening up to private courtyard
- Formal lounge area
- Double lockup garage
- Ducted Heating
- Split System Air conditioning
- Freshly Painted
- New Carpets
Don't miss out!

Description:
Affordable Townhouse
This charming and modern three-bedroom and two-bathroom townhouse is ideal for a young family, downsizer or astute investor. Downstairs you will find the formal light-filled lounge and tiled open-plan meals and kitchen area featuring stainless appliances, as well as a powder room, laundry and linen cupboard. The spacious master bedroom with ensuite, featuring a double vanity, and walk-in robe is located upstairs as are the other two generously sized bedrooms, both with built-in robes and the family bathroom. The private courtyard and double remote control garage can be easily accessed from the meals/kitchen area and is the perfect spot for outdoor entertainment as well as a secure place for children and pets to play.
Additional features include ducted reverse cycle cooling and heating, security alarm and rainwater tank.
With its fantastic location within walking distance to Dandenong Station and bus routes and just a few minutes' drive to Dandenong Plaza shopping centre, Cheltenham Road shopping/entertainment hub, schools, Dandenong Creek Reserve and easy access to Eastlink and Princes Highway, this home is an opportunity not to be missed.

A Perfect Start in a Prime Location!
Do not miss a rare opportunity to secure this spacious apartment ideal for first home buyers or investors in a prime central Dandenong location. This lovely, contemporary and low-maintenance double storey townhouse offering 3 bedrooms plus open study, stylish bathroom with dual access (incl. as main bedroom ensuite), 2 toilets, large open plan living with direct access to a private rear yard, immaculate kitchen featuring a dual sink, meals counter and quality stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, gas cooking, split system air conditioner, individual heaters in each bedroom and study, an intercom and an alarm system, a neat courtyard area and a single remote controlled lock up garage.

Description:
A modern & stylish low maintenance home in Metro Village
Located in the brilliantly designed Metro Village community where low maintenance housing meets practicality and a great location, this 2 storey corner home will please young families and investors alike. With Dandenong Creek and walking tracks at one end of the street, buses at the other and Dandenong train station nearby, the home is ideally positioned to give youan easy access to central Dandenong's shops, eateries and activities. The home features a lounge room, a tiled family/meals area with generous stainless steel equipped kitchen and the bonus of an upstairs living area that the kids will love. There are 3 robed bedrooms upstairs plus a study that could convert to a 4th bedroom on the ground floor. There's also an en suite and walk in wardrobe in the master bedroom, a family bathroom and an additional downstairs powder room. Ducted heating is also included and outside you will find a side accessed double remote garage and a grass free backyard that is easily maintained.

Description:
SOLD BY TEAM RAGHU FOR $575,000!
On a block of only two and positioned quietly at the rear, this three and a half year young unit offers a spacious home combined with easy care outdoor space. Walk everywhere with a brilliant location close to Dandenong Markets and Plaza, Robert Booth Reserve and sporting amenities, Dandenong Primary School, St John’s Regional College and Dandenong Hospital.
Welcomed by high ceilings, the versatile layout comprises of a large living and meals area plus a separate study or second dining space, a modern kitchen with loads of storage, three bedrooms, two bathrooms, separate WC and laundry. Premium inclusions such as stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances, porcelain tiles, downlights, ducted heating and evaporative cooling elevate this property straight to the top of the list!
Outside, a low maintenance courtyard, ideal for busy resident and tenants, features a timber deck for outdoor dining and entertaining, a handy garden shed, water tank and single garage with second tandem parking space.
Also enjoying convenient travel options via the Monash Freeway and Dandenong Bypass plus nearby public transport this home is set to appealing to a broad range of buyers so be sure to get in quick!
• Single storey unit at the rear of block – close to shops, schools, parks, sporting amenities, hospital, major road links and public transport
• Modern kitchen with stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances and plenty of cupboards
• Open plan living and meal sitting area, study/dining room, master with ensuite and walk in robe, two additional bedrooms, central bathroom, separate WC and laundry
• Secure low maintenance courtyard, timber deck, storage shed, water tank and single garage plus tandem car space
• High ceilings, porcelain tiles, ducted heating, evaporative cooling and downlights
Note: Every care has been taken to verify the accuracy of the details in this advertisement, however we cannot guarantee its correctness. Prospective purchasers are requested to take such action as is necessary, to satisfy themselves of any pertinent matters.

Description:
Move Straight In & Enjoy Great Accessibility
Sitting in a highly desirable pocket of Dandenong, this street facing unit is perfect for all first home buyers and small families. Fully renovated internally the 3 bedroom home offers an expansive open plan living and dining area, well connected kitchen which overlooks the living spaces, central family bathroom, 2 toilets and single lock up garage. The immaculate property comes equipped with an array of features including gas ducted heating, split system air conditioning, laminated timber floors through all living spaces and bedrooms, downlights, kitchen with modern stainless steel appliances including dishwasher and the north facing aspect of the property gives the home loads of natural light throughout. With only 2 dwellings on the block, there is no active owner’s corporation whilst the area is super quiet and extremely accessible to all of Dandenong’s important amenities including Hospital, Market, Plaza and schools (walking distance to Dandenong North Primary School and Dandenong High School). With no work required but to simply move in and enjoy, make sure you view this home before it is too late!
